              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--ultramarine);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">YLT</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">And sons of the stranger, who are joined to Jehovah, To serve Him, and to love the name of Jehovah, To be to Him for servants, Every keeper of the sabbath from polluting it, And those keeping hold on My covenant.</span></div>
